WEBVTT

1
00:00:05.666 --> 00:00:07.066
Where is this?

2
00:00:07.366 --> 00:00:09.466
Hey, miss, Mr. Lu brought you back

3
00:00:09.466 --> 00:00:11.100
You've been unconscious for three days.

4
00:00:20.366 --> 00:00:23.166
Who agreed to cut off the drug?

5
00:00:23.500 --> 00:00:26.166
Wait for me to come over now miss

6
00:00:27.366 --> 00:00:28.466
Hey.

7
00:00:29.533 --> 00:00:30.333
Xixi

8
00:00:31.300 --> 00:00:32.900
You are finally here.

9
00:00:33.466 --> 00:00:34.766
Stop the drug yourself

10
00:00:34.966 --> 00:00:36.866
Didn't you just force me to come?

11
00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:39.100
Is your life so worthless?

12
00:00:39.333 --> 00:00:41.200
Xixi mother

13
00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:44.966
I didn't mean to embarrass you

14
00:00:45.800 --> 00:00:47.600
I don't want to hear that.

15
00:00:48.166 --> 00:00:49.800
I just wanted to see it.

16
00:00:50.400 --> 00:00:52.300
How far can you go?

17
00:00:54.933 --> 00:00:56.666
Since you developed kidney disease

18
00:00:56.666 --> 00:00:58.400
I haven't had a good day.

19
00:00:58.866 --> 00:01:00.766
I dream about it

20
00:01:01.166 --> 00:01:03.200
Work hard to make money to cure you

21
00:01:03.866 --> 00:01:06.866
I work four jobs a day for what?

22
00:01:07.533 --> 00:01:10.366
I'm just for your high surgery fee.

23
00:01:10.700 --> 00:01:12.800
I dream of you being alive

24
00:01:14.466 --> 00:01:16.833
I would even give you my kidney

25
00:01:17.100 --> 00:01:19.833
I thought you were my whole world

26
00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.200
I thought

27
00:01:21.766 --> 00:01:24.766
You are my only relative in the world

28
00:01:24.866 --> 00:01:27.700
Sorry, it's all my fault.

29
00:01:28.133 --> 00:01:31.266
My fault, your apology, I don't accept it.

